48:00.053 --> 48:02.637
because what I have to say
must be handled

48:02.637 --> 48:04.720
with alacrity and care.

48:04.720 --> 48:06.679
With or without
your blessing,

48:06.679 --> 48:10.345
I'm making the allegations
against Revered Fields public.

48:10.345 --> 48:12.637
[all gasp and murmur]

48:12.637 --> 48:15.303
Siobhan, I know the position
you're in.

48:15.303 --> 48:16.845
We just have to recognize

48:16.845 --> 48:19.553
that if these charges
become headlines,

48:19.553 --> 48:21.970
our coalition
will be adversely affected.

48:21.970 --> 48:23.637
Not just from a funding
standpoint.

48:23.637 --> 48:25.845
I've deposed each victim,

48:25.845 --> 48:29.011
and these women are telling
God's truth.

48:29.011 --> 48:32.845
Now, I've been going to church
since I was a baby.

48:32.845 --> 48:35.929
And unless there's a bake sale,

48:35.929 --> 48:38.178
Sunday school or a toy drive,

48:38.178 --> 48:40.553
women are never included
in the church's decisions.

48:40.553 --> 48:44.053
Isn't this a chance
for a deeply sexist,

48:44.053 --> 48:48.136
male-dominated church
to rise up, to speak up,

48:48.136 --> 48:50.345
and make positive change for
all believers in Jesus Christ?

48:50.345 --> 48:51.553
[excited chatter]

48:51.553 --> 48:53.303
Reverend Fields
will fight you on this.

48:53.303 --> 48:54.595
An eye for an eye.

48:54.595 --> 48:56.637
I've confronted him.

48:56.637 --> 48:59.136
He refuses to resign.

48:59.136 --> 49:03.095
If we can't convince him today
to step aside,

49:03.095 --> 49:05.679
the court of public opinion
will decide.

49:05.679 --> 49:07.720
[all murmur]

49:07.720 --> 49:11.845
He did this to himself.

49:11.845 --> 49:13.679
These are his sins,
not ours.

49:13.679 --> 49:15.845
That's right.

49:15.845 --> 49:17.553
We don't have to pay for them.

49:18.804 --> 49:20.303
[door opens]

49:51.011 --> 49:52.512
[Jackie]
So, you going to eat those eggs

49:52.512 --> 49:53.637
or just play hockey with them?

49:53.637 --> 49:55.679
What happened
to you?

49:55.679 --> 49:58.053
Alcohol-induced haymaker.

49:58.053 --> 49:59.178
What about you?

50:00.595 --> 50:03.178
Hand of God.
Literally.

50:03.178 --> 50:04.804
I was hungry
when I ordered them,

50:04.804 --> 50:08.428
but the 20-minute lag just--
just killed my appetite.

50:08.428 --> 50:09.887
Mind if I do?

50:09.887 --> 50:11.804
Yeah. Yeah, go for it.

50:14.053 --> 50:16.512
So, when are you meeting
with Hook's lawyer?

50:16.512 --> 50:18.053
Tomorrow.

50:18.053 --> 50:19.762
Make his balls sweat.

50:19.762 --> 50:21.512
Oh, I intend to.

50:21.512 --> 50:24.387
We are inches from blowing
this case wide open.

50:24.387 --> 50:25.762
And then the fun begins.

50:25.762 --> 50:27.512
[chuckles]

50:27.512 --> 50:29.053
How's the Dupont?

50:30.387 --> 50:31.970
Well, you know,

50:31.970 --> 50:33.553
Jenny, she just...

50:33.553 --> 50:35.178
I'm tryin' to give her space.

50:35.178 --> 50:37.387
She just needs some time to,
you know, make peace.

50:37.387 --> 50:39.053
With you?

50:41.095 --> 50:43.011
You and your wife
ever go ten rounds?

50:43.011 --> 50:44.470
[scoffs]
Ten.

50:44.470 --> 50:46.220
I never last to the tenth.

50:46.220 --> 50:47.595
I used to.

50:47.595 --> 50:49.220
-[laughs]
-[cell phone rings]

