51:07.053 --> 51:08.762
Jackie, where's our daughter?

51:08.762 --> 51:10.095
When was the last time
you saw her?

51:11.845 --> 51:14.845
Uh...yesterday, maybe?

51:14.845 --> 51:17.512
I don't know!
Oh, shit.

51:17.512 --> 51:18.887
Ja...

51:18.887 --> 51:20.679
Jackie, you've got
to find her, okay?

51:20.679 --> 51:22.595
Yeah. Okay.

51:22.595 --> 51:24.011
I'm going to find her.

51:24.011 --> 51:26.553
You stay by the phone,
all right?

51:27.679 --> 51:29.261
[dials]

51:30.303 --> 51:31.595
Come fucking on.

51:31.595 --> 51:33.804
Yeah, hey.
This is Rohr.

51:33.804 --> 51:36.470
I need a BOLO
on a white female,

51:36.470 --> 51:38.553
brown hair, 16 years old,

51:38.553 --> 51:41.970
110 pounds, 5'2".

51:41.970 --> 51:43.929
Name is...

51:43.929 --> 51:46.053
Benedetta Rohr.

51:46.053 --> 51:47.762
It's my daughter.

51:49.679 --> 51:50.970
All right.

51:50.970 --> 51:52.762
Jesus, Jackie,
what can I do?

52:00.845 --> 52:02.428
You know, I'm hearing
a lot about

52:02.428 --> 52:04.303
the top echelon
informant program.

52:04.303 --> 52:06.136
How that's going awry.
and there's nobody watching.

52:06.136 --> 52:08.387
-Not a good time, Michaela.
-Am I rattling the cage--?

52:08.387 --> 52:09.970
Get fucking lost!

52:11.512 --> 52:14.804
That tells me that I'm rattling
the right cage.

52:14.804 --> 52:16.887
[debris clattering]

52:30.970 --> 52:33.178
Gee, that ain't shit, huh?

52:34.845 --> 52:36.929
No. It's less than shit.

52:40.011 --> 52:42.261
Birds in the house, bro.

52:43.178 --> 52:45.136
[sighs] Bad Irish luck.

52:45.136 --> 52:47.220
Born white,
and every fucking moolie

52:47.220 --> 52:49.178
thinks we get a pass
on the miserable shit in life.

52:49.178 --> 52:51.136
The fuck do we do?

52:51.136 --> 52:53.845
What if Ma does need
that operation?

52:55.553 --> 52:57.136
Fuck it.

